title: NFL Power Rankings: Chiefs remain king, Packers best in NFC, Seahawks outside the Top 5? (Football 10/28)
description:
Wednesday means it's time for Will Brinson to hit his favorite sound effect. No, not Randy Bullock missing and Kevin Harlan's glorious voice...It's the Brady Quinn Football Show air horn! This week, Brady shares his Power Rankings, focusing on the Top 5 (6:00) and Bottom 5 (24:15). The Chiefs remain the obvious choice at number one (even if Pete Prisco says otherwise). After that it gets tricky. Brinson is high on the Bucs to win the NFC, but BQ has a different team ahead of them. Where will the league's last unbeaten team be slotted? Not as high as you'd think! The guys then shift towards the bottom of the league, otherwise known as the race for Trevor Lawrence.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
